messageBody:
Bauduin Raphael wrote:

> Hi,
>
> Can someone help me by giving an example of how to use a ResultPrinter?
> Most methods are protected, does that mean I should extend it to use it?
> I have a TestResult object, but I don't know how to print it to the
> standard output....

I guess don't use ResultPrinter: ask the TestResult object for the
information you want to print, then print those objects yourself. It
appears that one did not design ResultPrinter to be used on its own.
